Mom reports none. The presence of these would suggest the presence of IgE to mediate these processes.
Did PJ have a newborn screen? Was it normal?
Mom reports a normal newborn screen, as far as she knows. An abnormal newborn screen would pick up severe combined immunodeficiency (SCID).
